@startuml
actor Admin as Actor
participant SemesterList
participant SemesterController
participant SemesterRepositories
participant Database

Admin as Actor -> SemesterList : Access semester list
SemesterList -> SemesterController : getAllSemesters()
SemesterController -> SemesterRepositories : Fetch all semesters
SemesterRepositories -> Database : Query semesters
Database --> SemesterRepositories : Return semester data
SemesterRepositories --> SemesterController : Semesters with counts
SemesterController --> SemesterList : Semester list

Admin as Actor -> SemesterList : Select a semester
SemesterList -> SemesterController : getUsersBySemester(semesterId)
SemesterController -> SemesterRepositories : Fetch users for semester
SemesterRepositories -> Database : Query users
Database --> SemesterRepositories : Return user data
SemesterRepositories --> SemesterController : Users with details
SemesterController --> SemesterList : User details

SemesterList --> Admin as Actor : Display updated semester view
@enduml
